      <talk_paragraph index="001" image="" itemindex="">
         <talk_question mid="3"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>
What are you doing here?</html>]]></talk_question>
      </talk_paragraph>
      <talk_paragraph index="prologue_makina01" image="" itemindex="">
         <talk_answer link_index="prologue_makina02" mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>Who are you? Where am I?</html>]]></talk_answer>
         <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$Mysterious Tiger Man$<BR>Splendid! Those are some great moves you've got there!<BR>I've finally found a disciple to pass down my One-armed Kung Fu! </html>]]></talk_question>
      </talk_paragraph>
      <talk_paragraph index="prologue_makina02" image="" itemindex="">
         <talk_answer link_index="prologue_makina03" mid="38"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#2b2723>Why would I do that...?</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
         <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Mysterious Tiger Man$<BR>Ehem. My name is Xiaolong and you're near Prairie Town right now. <BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Xiaolong suddenly looks around.)</FONT><BR>Hmm… this place is too dangerous for a chat. Let's continue talking in Prairie Town.</html>]]></talk_question>
      </talk_paragraph>
      <talk_paragraph index="prologue_makina03" image="" itemindex="">
         <talk_answer link_index="prologue_makina04" mid="39"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#2b2723>A pass? </FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
         <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Why? <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Xiaolong flusters as he didn't expect such a question from you.)</FONT><BR>Well… nothing good will come out of staying here… Don't tell me you don't have a pass. </html>]]></talk_question>
      </talk_paragraph>
      <talk_paragraph index="prologue_makina04" image="" itemindex="">
         <talk_answer link_index="prologue_makina05" mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>Oh… okay...</html>]]></talk_answer>
         <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Hybrids like us need passes to go to other towns.<BR>Krrang… I guess you don't have one since you're keeping quiet. <BR>Well then… You should just sneak in! Come right to me and avoid eye contact with the mayor or the other people in town!</html>]]></talk_question>
      </talk_paragraph>
      <talk_paragraph index="prologue_makina05" image="" itemindex="">
         <talk_answer link_index="next" mid="41"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#2b2723>(Xiaolong vanishes in a second.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
         <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>I'll tell you more in Prairie Town!</html>]]></talk_question>
